#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In these modules, you can configure various aspects of &konqueror;’s file "
"manager functionality."
msgstr ""
"V teh modulih lahko konfigurirate različne vidike funkcionalnosti "
"upravljalnika datotek &konqueror;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror;’s web browser functionality has its <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/"
"khtml-behavior/index.html\">own configuration modules</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Funkcionalnost spletnega brskalnika &konqueror; ima svoje <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/khtml-behavior/index.html\">lastne module konfiguracije</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Misc Options"
msgstr "Razne možnosti"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open folders in separate windows"
msgstr "Odprite mape v ločenih oknih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when you "
"open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder’s contents in the "
"current window."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo ustvarjeno novo okno &konqueror;, ko odprete "
"mapo, namesto da bi preprosto prikazal vsebino te mape v trenutnem oknu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show “Delete” menu entries which bypass the trashcan"
msgstr "Prikaži vnose »Izbriši« v menijih, ki obidejo smetnjak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this if you want <quote>Delete</quote> menu commands to be displayed "
"on the desktop and in the file manager’s context menus. You can always "
"delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling <guimenuitem>Move to "
"Trash</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Označite to, če želite, da so menijski ukazi <quote>Izbriši</quote> "
"prikazani na namizju in v kontekstnih menijih upravljalnika datotek. "
"Datoteke lahko vedno izbrišete tako, da držite &Shift; med klicanjem "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni v koš</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings for &konqueror;’s file manager mode on the <guilabel>View "
"Modes</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Services</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>General</guilabel> and <guilabel>Trash</guilabel> pages "
"are used by &dolphin; as well."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve za način upravitelja datotek &konqueror; v <guilabel>Načinih "
"pogleda</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigaciji</guilabel>, <guilabel>Storitvah</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> in <guilabel>Smetnjak</guilabel> "
"uporablja prav tako &dolphin;."

